```bash\nmysqldump -u root -p mydatabase > mydatabase_backup.sql\n```\n\n#### 导入整个数据库\n```bash\nmysql -u root -p mydatabase < mydatabase_backup.sql\n```\n\n#### 导出特定表\n```bash\nmysqldump -u root -p mydatabase mytable > mytable_backup.sql\n```\n\n#### 导入特定表\n```bash\nmysql -u root -p mydatabase < mytable_backup.sql\n```\n\n### 5. 注意事项\n- 确保你有足够的权限执行导出和导入操作。\n- 导入时，目标数据库必须已经存在。如果不存在，需要先创建数据库：\n  ```sql\n  CREATE DATABASE 数据库名;\n  ```\n\n通过这些命令，你可以快速导出和导入MySQL数据库。',' ','','',3,0,1,1741045487,'127.0.0.1',' '),(16,'86f6803e-3a5d-4606-a42d-612d353ad727',15,1,'rust fs临时文件保存','','','','   ![paste_image.png](/upload/images/b356ac0f-4b99-475b-b58e-93012f98c3ef.png)',' ','','',0,0,0,1741045920,'127.0.0.1',' '),(17,'c68092d3-eb04-4845-8ccf-1b8f1724e791',16,1,'gitee 代码迁移','','','','![paste_image.png](/upload/images/b40b82b5-6d62-4867-908b-008dcb24ad60.png)\nhttps://gitee.com/zhoutengteng/zttccf_space\n```\ngit config --global user.name \"zhoutengteng\"\ngit config --global user.email \"865998332@qq.com\"\n创建 git 仓库:\n\nmkdir zttccf_space\ncd zttccf_space\ngit init \ntouch README.md\ngit add README.md\ngit commit -m \"first commit\"\ngit remote add origin https://gitee.com/zhoutengteng/zttccf_space.git\ngit push -u origin \"master\"\n已有仓库?\n\ncd existing_git_repo\ngit remote add origin https://gitee.com/zhoutengteng/zttccf_space.git\ngit push -u origin \"master\"\n```',' ','','',1,0,1,1741048140,'127.0.0.1',' ');
